# Already-stripped content — running the helper again is a no-op

See (loom-internal reference) for the original analysis.

The ml package directory tests/integration/test_foo.py covers the
guard. The dataflow package (`src/dataflow/adapters/mongodb.py`) is
the canonical example.

Diagnose with `gh api repos/<org>/<repo>/actions/runs`. Sibling SDK
references are described as the sibling SDK's `.claude/rules/foo.md`
once cleaned.
